# Relationships to illustrate hubs, high-degree, central, connector, intermediary, multiplex, super nodes

<https://example.com/hubNode> noria:elementManagedBy <https://example.com/NetworkOperations> ;
  noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/connectionCount> .

<https://example.com/highDegreeNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/connectionCount> .

<https://example.com/centralNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/centralityScore> .

<https://example.com/connectorNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/segmentConnections> .

<https://example.com/intermediaryNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/dataFlowRate> .

<https://example.com/multiplexNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/streamCount> .

<https://example.com/superNode> noria:structuralElementObservable <https://example.com/observable/aggregationLevel> .

# All nodes are linked with at least one relation, no isolated nodes included.
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> .
